//Stringhe per il 'fragment home' Welcome to Savent! We have created this app with the intent to contain the virus and facilitate the creation and sharing of groups and events of various kinds. We help make these meetings safe by making it possible for non-contagious people to participate in events to avoid the spread of the virus. Your privacy with us is safe. The information you enter will not be disclosed to third parties and no one will be aware of your personal data when you communicate the result of the swab performed by you. Find out how our app works How the app works Healthcare organizations can subscribe to the app and forward to the patient, via email or other, the result of the swab marked with an identification code. This unique code generated can be used by the user to share their health condition anonymously. The application keeps track of all your contacts locally, by exchanging identification codes via Bluetooth Low Energy. Savent notifies users of any close encounters with positive subjects without revealing the identity and location of the contact. You can disable the tracking feature directly from the settings or by swiping a hand across the top of the screen.
